SQL_STMT_U.val: select cast (sum (SCHI.SCHI_FACTORINGCOMMC) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum (SCHI.SCHI_INSURANCECOMMC) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum (SCHI.SCHI_ADDITIONALCOMMC) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum (SCHI.SCHI_CREDNOTESADDCOMMC) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/SCHI SCHI where SCHI.SCHI_SCHT_NO = :2 for fetch only
select count(*) from :1/SCHI SCHI where SCHI.SCHI_SCHT_NO = :2 and SCHI.SCHI_INVAMOUNTI < 0 and SCHI.SCHI_INVDELETED = 'N' and SCHI.SCHI_MANUALCHANGE = 'Y' for fetch only
